                      MOVE WS-NAME   TO NAME10O
                      MOVE WS-STATUS TO STATS10O
                      MOVE WS-ACTAMT TO ACTU10O
                      MOVE ZEROES    TO PAID10O
              END-EVALUATE

              ADD 1 TO WS-TEMP-INDEX

           END-PERFORM
           EXEC CICS SEND MAP('AGCT') MAPSET('AGCT') ERASE
           END-EXEC
           IF EIBCALEN = 0
           EXEC CICS RETURN
                     TRANSID('TACT')
                     COMMAREA(WS-COMMAREA)
                     LENGTH(LENGTH OF WS-COMMAREA)
           END-EXEC
           ELSE
           EXEC CICS RETURN
                     TRANSID('TACT')
                     COMMAREA(DFHCOMMAREA)
                     LENGTH(LENGTH OF DFHCOMMAREA)
           END-EXEC.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      * NEXT PAGE
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
       NEXT-PAGE.

           IF CA-INDEX + 10 > CA-TOTAL
              MOVE 'REACHED BOTTOM' TO MSGO
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              ADD 10 TO CA-INDEX
           END-IF.
